# Implementation Plan - Student Dashboard Migration & Test Conduct Alignment

This plan addresses the migration of the student dashboard to Livewire while ensuring the "Test Conduct" feature preserves 100% parity with the legacy version. As requested, legacy controllers will be analyzed deeply, and only non-essential, redundant methods will be considered for removal, while preserving the old dashboard for potential future use.

## 0. Pre-requisite: Commit Checkpoint
Before any changes, we will perform a git commit to mark the current state.
**Commit Message**: `chore: deep analysis of student controllers and preparation for Livewire migration v2`

