## 2. Test Conduct Alignment (OnlineTestRunner)

The following features from the old `start-test.blade.php` will be replicated in `OnlineTestRunner`:

### Phase A: Instruction & Terms Enforcement
-   [ ] Add `termsAccepted` and `privacyAccepted` properties to `OnlineTestRunner`.
-   [ ] Modify Blade to wire these to checkboxes and disable "Start Test" until both are checked.

### Phase B: Global Question Palette
-   [ ] Re-implement the palette to show **ALL questions from ALL sections** in a single grid (standard in competitive exams).
-   [ ] Color Coding logic:
    -   **Gray (Base-300)**: Not Visited.
    -   **Red (Error)**: Visited but not Answered.
    -   **Green (Success)**: Answered.
    -   **Warning/Star**: Marked for Review.
-   [ ] Ensure clicking a question in the palette correctly switches both the section and the question index.

### Phase C: Summary & Review Mode
-   [ ] Implement a "Summary" view (replacing the old `loc-Modal`) that shows final counts before submission.
-   [ ] Ensure "Save & Next" on the last question of a section automatically jumps to the next section OR the summary view.

## 3. Preservation Strategy
-   Maintain `routes/student_old.php` under the `/old` prefix defined in `bootstrap/app.php`.
-   Rename classes or namespace them if they cause conflicts (though currently they are in separate namespaces: `App\Livewire\Student` vs `App\Http\Controllers\Student`).

